== Higan ==

Higan (formerly known as bsnes) is a Nintendo multi-system emulator that focuses on accuracy and clean code above all else. It never uses speed or compatibility hacks. As a result, the minimum system requirements are higher than with other emulators. View a YouTube demo [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eFfa7VXdcxc here].

It currently supports the following systems:

* Nintendo Entertainment System/Famicom
* Super Nintendo Entertainment System/Super Famicom
* Game Boy
* Game Boy Color
* Game Boy Advance

Higan also supports the following subsystems:

* Super Game Boy
* BS-X Satellaview
* Sufami Turbo


