Yabause is a Sega Saturn emulator with the following features:

* Booting games from CD-ROM and ISO files.
* Booting games with either an emulated or original BIOS.
* Screenshot support.
* Save game backups.
* Cheat system.
* Fullscreen playing.
* Multiple debugging options.
* Joystick support.
* Region select.

